### Option 1: The "Sidebar" Description (Short & Punchy)

*Use this for the "About" section on the right-hand side of your GitHub repository page.*

> A comprehensive guide to Prompt Engineering using Google Cloud Vertex AI and Gemini 2.5. Covers zero-shot/few-shot prompting, hallucination guardrails, and optimizing LLM responses for production.

